            <title>[LU-9549] MR: assert on ln_state during shutdown</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9549</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When shutting down, we could still be processing messages. lnet_parse() can be called, while simoultaneously the ln_state is changed from running to stopping. We need to handle this case with proper locking.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
